# packages/design-tokens/.tmp/.gitignore
# Whitelist: everything under .tmp is local, task-scoped scratch (Figma
# snapshots + per-task JSON data) and must NOT be committed. The only
# exception is scripts/ — the committed Figma pull/generators — so agents
# don't rebuild them every run. See ../AGENTS.md and ../context/figma-sync.md.
#
# Kept under .tmp (not promoted to a real workspace dir) until the pipeline
# is settled.

# Ignore everything by default.
*

# Opt the committed generators back in (dir first, then contents).
!.gitignore
!scripts/
!scripts/**
